        <h3>making 20 minutes mean more</h3>
        <p>Twennie is named after the Pareto Principle, which states that 20 percent of our effort produces 80 percent of our results. Our mission is to make the 20 percent produce more. Our learners might have 20 minutes or less to learn something that makes a real difference in their work, and Twennie is committed to making that 20 minutes count.</p>
