        <p>Twennie gives you the chance to write your own learning content, but also to combine learning content you find in the Twennie library into new units. For instance, if you find three units and each one contains only select content you want to share with your team, you can take the needed content and combine it in one new unit. No need for them to sift through what's not needed.</p>
